column5: Hey guys are any east tribs fishable? With gas prices what they are i would like to be sure i can fish before i go.  thanks for the info
I doubt you'll get many responses except for 'Go find out for yourself', lol.
Ehhh, at least he doens't  have 1 post expecting to get answers... but yeah, go find out yourself or move closer!  My guess is that they're blown.
lol i actually thought twice about asking.
lol!  I think the consensus is that they aren't in very good shape right now

ganaraska river is high but fishable . they caught some fish today but not in great numbers.  if your on facebook check out ganaraskafishway    for reports of fishing and how far along is the rainbow run
maybe by the middle of the week, supposed to warm as well.
Alright, Thank you guys for replying. Maybe I`ll save the gas and go next weekend instead.
